short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chromium extension to move tabs around the browser's windows.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps to order your tabs by adding options to page's context menu, and by adding keyboard shortcuts to speed up the process. 

The tab can be moved to a new window, to another window (if you have precisely two windows open) or to one of your other windows (you will choose which one). You can also move all the tabs at once. 

Supported keyboard shortcuts:
* Alt+O -- moves the current tab to a new window
* Alt+P -- moves the current tab to another window (if exists)
* Alt+L -- moves all the tabs to another window (if exists)
